            <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m Zhuma, an automation major at Harbin Institute of Technology (Shenzhen).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;experience&#34;&gt;Experience&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2023 - Present&lt;/strong&gt;： Undergraduate student at HIT Shenzhen, Automation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-this-blog&#34;&gt;About This Blog&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This blog mainly shares my daily life, and occasionally some tech-related stuff (maybe 😂). The fundamental reason I built this blog is that I&amp;rsquo;ve always thought having a personal homepage is a cool thing. The immediate trigger was reading &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://speechlesspanda.github.io/2026/03/01/%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%B6%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%84%9F/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    &gt;this article&lt;/a&gt; which inspired me 😂 (though I first saw it on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://hoa.moe/blog/thoughts-from-a-college-student-with-one-and-a-half-years-of-practice&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    &gt;HOA&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;blockquote&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note&lt;/strong&gt;: This blog is primarily in Chinese. Some content may not be available in English.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;contact&#34;&gt;Contact&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/beilu-zhuma&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    &gt;beilu-zhuma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email&lt;/strong&gt;：18755667356@163.com&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;blockquote&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Do not fear the infinity of truth — every inch of progress brings its own joy.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xD;&#xA;</description>
